Class MapMimeTypeCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.nda.elasticsearch.load.AbstractMimeTypeCache
      • nl.naturalis.nda.elasticsearch.load.MapMimeTypeCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, MimeTypeCache

    public class MapMimeTypeCache
extends AbstractMimeTypeCache
    Implementation of MimeTypeCache that uses a TreeMap as backbone for the mime type cache. This is the default implementation used by the import programs.
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman
